title: ISic001774. I.Sicily inscription 001774
body:
Facsimile Images

πρὸ ε´ καλ(ανδῶν) Αὐγούσ(των)
Εὔκτη τελεύ-
τᾷ ἐτῶν
δέκα´ (Χριστό)ς

Apparatus criticus

Text after Orsi 1893

English translation

Eukte passed away 5 days before the Kalends of August (aged) ten years. Christos.
